<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>- ص -<span class="c5"> ابن داب:</span> عيسى بن يزيد <span class="c2">(٢)</span> <span class="c4">[٥٩٦٢]</span>.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
